{
  "stem": "16473.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I now know about Jesus and if I leave that knowledge behind, then what will happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said go talk to Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Mann at Sinai Temple, and I did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Mann looked at me and he said, is your mother Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Is your father Jewish?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What are you doing over there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Come here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I went, and I also found it very interesting, until after confirmation, then I started going to temple.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I start perceiving-- now that this is perception-- I start perceiving that the man is posturing on stage.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "People are wearing their best furs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You can't go to a service, a high service, unless you've paid a whole bunch of money, didn't seem right to me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I floundered around for a real long time, looking at different religions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "What was your family's reaction to this?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To my looking at other religions?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't-- they were not bothered by it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was with my father, who was the continental Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother was in Europe, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] she probably thought my grandfather would turn over in his grave.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I forgot to tell you that after the war, because she couldn't have a Christmas branch, I got a Christmas tree, fully lit, all the presents and everything.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my mother was not bound to the Jewish religion, as such.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, she was bound and she-- but she was rebelling, I guess, is the story.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I did not get any flack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother, when she came to America, she had Passover dinners and invited my children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But didn't I think when the children came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think she did it before that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I had-- that-- that year that I had Christmas, I had Hanukkah and Christmas.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
